flowchart LR
    A["Dashboard\n(Tap a Wheel)"] -->|"Choose Stock"| B["Ticker Thesis View\n(See Thesis + Wheel)"]

    B -->|"Tap Idle Dot\n(New Contract)"| C["Trade Type\n(New CSP)"]
    B -->|"Tap Active Dot\n(Existing Contract)"| D["Trade Type\n(Based on Phase)"]

    C --> E["Trade Details"]
    D --> E

    E -->|"Strike, Premium,\nExpiry, Delta"| F["Smart Nudges\n(Live Feedback)"]

    F -->|"Deviation?"| G{"Aligned with\nStrategy & Thesis?"}

    G -->|"Yes"| I["Save Trade"]
    G -->|"No"| H["Enter Reason\nfor Deviation"]
    H --> I

    I -->|"Dot Moves on Ring\nHero Metrics Update"| B
